page.title: 17TRADE-ROSE GREEN
page.content: There are three small food supermarkets,one of which also sells magazines,stationery,sweets and cigarettes.We have seven food shops and three restaurants.There are two Chinese take aways one of which is a restaurant.The post office is also a general store and sells stationery and food.Jennings is a toy shop,a shoe shop and a printers.We have quite a few combined shops such as the hair_dressers selling jewellery and another selling wool.There is a video hire shop,a garage,electrical shop and a chemist.There is a pet shop,a garden hardware shop,wine shop,dry cleaners, launderette and bakers.a shop which sells baby clothes while another is trading in antiques.
